title: Deaf Activist Brandi Rarus Speaks at Chapel (University of Mary Hardin-Baylor)
text: ( Source : University of Mary Hardin-Baylor ) Belton, Texas - Deaf activist and author Brandi Rarus will be the guest speaker at the University of Mary Hardin-Baylor on Wednesday, October 7, at 10 and 11 a.m. in the W. W. Walton Chapel . Rarus
